{"tid":786870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[seed]太上老君偷情鐵扇公主生下紅孩兒？中國電影引共憤被禁","createTime":"2018-08-20T08:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T04:34:01.000Z","uid":54373,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"805d4c1bf871aded6f5e22614800e4804d3b0a0e","tid":786870,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpTiwzQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpTiwzQE.jpg&h=f1fa4aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國網絡電影《天篷元帥之大鬧天宮》，情節被指控低俗，遭到中國道教聲討，已經被下架禁播。圖為電影情節之一是太上老君火辣偷情鐵扇公主。（圖擷取自網路）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國網絡電影《天篷元帥之大鬧天宮》，情節之一是太上老君偷情鐵扇公主，生下紅孩兒，據報導，誇張的劇情遭到道教界怒轟，中國道教協會開會議聲討，指控「貶低醜化道教神仙，嚴重傷害道教界感情」，這部影片已被下架禁播。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，這部電影被稱是以《西遊記》為藍本，並結合民間傳說及網絡小說等，重新創作成電影劇本，拍成電影，今年5月中旬在中國網絡平台播放。<br />\n<br />\n但是，從播放之後，即引來大量網友砲轟「低俗不堪」，劇情是講天篷元帥（即豬八戒前世）無意間捲入天庭大陰謀，為救好友大鵬及心上人玉兔，聯合眾妖仙大鬧天庭，但情節之中，有天篷元帥看到嫦娥洗澡，還化成螃蟹躲進洗澡水裡；太上老君變「小王」與牛魔王妻子鐵公主偷情，生下了紅孩兒，更有兩仙在煉丹房火辣偷情的場景。<br />\n<br />\n針對這誇張低俗情節，中國道教協會在本月15日發表聲明，指「該電影貶低醜化道教神仙，嚴重傷害道教界感情，引發道教界人士和信教群眾強烈反應」，要求依法處理；電影製片公司及優酷等多名高層在強大的輿論壓力下，8月17日專程到中國道教協會道歉，還表示已把相關影片及圖文下架、屏蔽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.read01.com/SIG=38tlr0h/304a6e344e566a647039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.read01.com%2FSIG%3D38tlr0h%2F304a6e344e566a647039.jpg&h=563a1aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.read01.com/SIG=h60tp9/304a6e344e564a6d7030.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.read01.com%2FSIG%3Dh60tp9%2F304a6e344e564a6d7030.jpg&h=819c9dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看太上老君和鐵扇公主，圖片中可以看到這一幕，這麼太上老君成肌肉男了，變得這麼men了。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/yOJ44mD.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FyOJ44mD.html&d=LDRqnxBZ3bCscDMT3EvQtACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=70549f0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/yOJ44mD.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.read01.com/SIG=ar4ghb/304a6e344e5662427142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.read01.com%2FSIG%3Dar4ghb%2F304a6e344e5662427142.jpg&h=e6e2872f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太上老君跟鐵扇公主私會不說，還跟她生了個紅孩兒，這種劇情已讓觀眾不敢直視，最可怕的是倆人用這種方式演繹，會不會讓觀眾感到低俗呢？<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/yOJ44mD.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FyOJ44mD.html&d=LDRqnxBZ3bCscDMT3EvQtACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=70549f0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/yOJ44mD.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i3.read01.com/SIG=1p2rdvu/304a6e344e5673594c44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi3.read01.com%2FSIG%3D1p2rdvu%2F304a6e344e5673594c44.jpg&h=55382584&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15fedd4e69047924c838a7ae500e0f7414bafa1f","tid":786870,"uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0sZxI5c0p64/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F0sZxI5c0p64%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=29d321e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/15330428309457bdd8e3cf1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F15330428309457bdd8e3cf1&h=83a95bb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4923e273a6b6339551dcd58ef9456b6aef1d2fd","tid":786870,"uid":54373,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1533043654957e2f7577dbf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F1533043654957e2f7577dbf&h=a4ec3848&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"971e469dace201760416ec25d15c7f764411cc75","tid":786870,"uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ytimg.googleusercontent.com/vi/miAYoFom94U/mqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fytimg.googleusercontent.com%2Fvi%2FmiAYoFom94U%2Fmqdefault.jpg&h=5071f58c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b76030edcd1b9d7b64c6481f22862381925aaca8","tid":786870,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070007685e8e466c3ff1b71cd6f3db3be5d71e7c","tid":786870,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:47:49.000Z","msg":"愈禁咪愈多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6106646f33b0d5ab85ba2ac700ee339684058c","tid":786870,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:48:09.000Z","msg":"太上老君邊位嚟？"},{"pid":"44efe113084098ec5ae1dfa94c942eb48646b562","tid":786870,"uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"070007685e8e466c3ff1b71cd6f3db3be5d71e7c","tid":786870,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:47:49.000Z","msg":"愈禁咪愈多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:48:46.000Z","msg":"終於有自主研發4仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d147e4413c4b7b62acef2dc0e19796f18ec7f72","tid":786870,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=3eevh15/ctp-vzntr/153348591016278q8384o97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3eevh15%2Fctp-vzntr%2F153348591016278q8384o97.jpg&h=a8ca5718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇中太上老君和鐵扇公主偷情，還生了紅孩兒，兩人在煉丹爐前做愛，裸露的尺寸之大讓人目瞪口呆，而且煉丹其目的是為了壯陽。<br />\n<br />\n喜劇演員程野以及九五後小花景璇領銜主演，為保證「笑果」更有 苑瓊丹、黃一飛、梁家仁、程思涵等一眾周星馳御用配角傾情助陣。"},{"pid":"04bfcd0e682146cc78c14806d9b93cfb520de7c1","tid":786870,"uid":99028,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":3,"re